♪Dare not speak, dare not gaze♪

222
00:11:40,594 --> 00:11:44,634
♪Yet I crave your glance♪

223
00:11:44,634 --> 00:11:48,442
♪Time, leaving many pasts behind♪

224
00:11:48,442 --> 00:11:52,498
♪Desolation follows splendor♪

225
00:11:52,498 --> 00:11:56,459
♪Only after seeing enough
worldly absurdity♪

226
00:11:56,466 --> 00:12:00,078
♪Will I kiss your face♪

227
00:12:00,078 --> 00:12:04,186
♪Never forgotten, hope you've been well♪

228
00:12:04,186 --> 00:12:06,810
♪Borrowing the first ray
of spring light♪

229
